Usage: selectBusGuideSegment [-help] -box {x1 y1 x2 y2} -layer {id | id1:id2}
                             -netGroup <netGroup>

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-box {x1 y1 x2 y2}       # The bounding box of the bus guide segment
                         # (box, required)
-layer {id | id1:id2}    # layer id or a layer range (string, required)
-netGroup <netGroup>     # NetGroup name (string, required)